<footer class="container main-footer">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
        <h4>To check validation on the form above do the following:</h4>
        <p>Type more than 20 characters into the First Name field</p>
        <p>Type more than 20 characters into the Last Name field</p>
        <p>Add 6 digits consisting of letters, numbers, & special characters to the Zip Code field</p>
        <p>Add letters and numbers to the Phone Number field and attempt to use this format: xxx-xxx-xxxx</p>
        <p>Enter an invalid email address into the Email Address field (i.e. somename.com)</p>
        <p>Leave the Checkbox unchecked</p>
        <p>Click Submit</p>
    </div>
</footer>
